WEBVTT

00:06:26.840 --> 00:06:31.456
Girls nowadays get their periods
in classes six and seven,

00:06:31.480 --> 00:06:33.096
but our educational curriculum

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:36.920
teaches girls about periods
only in standard eight and nine.

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:39.360
And since it is a taboo,

00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:43.440
teachers still
skip the subject altogether.

00:06:44.840 --> 00:06:49.096
So school does not
teach girls about periods,

00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:51.256
parents don't talk about it.

00:06:51.280 --> 00:06:52.680
Where do the girls go?

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:56.520
Two decades ago and now --

00:06:57.120 --> 00:06:58.400
nothing has changed.